</answer>
<answer fraction="100" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B)
</p>]]></text>
<feedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B): Correct
</p>]]></text>
</feedback>
